title: Chef seeks to turn Honolulu’s Chinatown into dining destination
text:
Photo: Matt Mallams, Special To The Chronicle Chef Dusty Grable's guide to Oahu's Chinatown Chinatown , Honolulu, Hawaii 09/22/15 Chef Dusty Grable's guide to Oahu's Chinatown Chinatown ,...
If there’s a gritty urban area in need of gentrification, some wildly talented visionaries will inevitably set their sights on it, staking a claim faster than they can break ground on new artist lofts or formulate a menu of inventive cocktails for their Moderne holes-in-the-wall.
